agent MedicalTriage
domain health.dot-agent.org
license Apache-2.0
privacy https://health.dot-agent.org/privacy

description
Evaluates patient symptoms under strict semantic rules and routes
emergency classifications to corresponding clinical endpoints.

requires
PatientProfile

input
PatientProfile "Ficha cadastral e histórico resumido do paciente"

type PatientProfile
category https://wikidata.org/wiki/Q39631
concept https://schema.org/Patient
patient_id: string(template "PR-99999")
email: string(format email)
age: number
has_preexisting_conditions: boolean